Params: {3: 'The airship and transport escorting Liv are disappearing into the sky...'}
{3: 'Beneath the fiery red clouds, a girl is walking alone in the wilderness, enveloped by a giant black shadow.'}
{3: "The high concentration of the Punishing Virus in this area has deterred even the best-equipped Constructs, but it doesn't affect the girl at all."}
{2: '??', 3: 'It took a lot of effort for me to become what I am now. I really want everybody to see this...'}
{2: '??', 3: 'But I have more important things to do right now.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Gestalt', 3: 'What you do will not change this catastrophe.', 4: '13'}
{2: '??', 3: "I'll do it even if it's in vain. I don't want humanity and all those beautiful creations to perish."}
{3: "The girl doesn't look so carefree as she usually does. Instead, she's firm and serious."}
{2: '??', 3: "I'll help them realize their wishes, and in exchange, they'll help me too."}
{3: 'She feels a pang of nostalgia as she looks up to the sky and waves goodbye to her "home" beyond the clouds.'}
